- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possibility because the paper introduces a diagrammatic model of computation that can be seen as a type of data structure. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possibility because the paper mentions the use of the proposed model for protocols, which can be related to game theory. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possibility because the paper introduces a new way of representing computations using diagrams, which can be seen as a type of programming language.
